fit <- lm(mpg~factor(am)+factor(cyl)+disp+hp+drat+wt+qsec+factor(vs)+factor(gear)+factor(carb), data = mtcars)
Coef <- coef(summary(fit))[1:2,]
round(dfbetas(fit)[,2],3) -> beta
plot(beta)

round(hatvalues(fit),3) -> hav
plot(hav)

par(mfrow=c(2,2))
plot(fit)
